      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be validated under a formal quality management system with documented version control, issue tracking, and regression testing appropriate for Class III device software.",
      "rationale": "Version control and basic regression tests are in place, but no formal QMS audit has been completed and issue tracking is informal. Achieved level 2 is two steps below the required level 4 for MRL 5 Class III device use."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
