      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification must demonstrate formal order-of-accuracy testing against manufactured solutions for all governing equations used in the hemolysis model.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was performed only for the Navier-Stokes solver; the hemolysis transport scalar equation was not subjected to manufactured solution verification. Achieved level 2 versus required level 4."
    },
    {
