      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be performed on geometry, operating conditions, and fluid properties that are representative of the VAD COU with documented similarity arguments for any differences.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic pump geometry rather than the actual VAD geometry. No formal similarity argument is provided for the geometric and operational differences. Achieved level 2 is three steps below required level 5."
    },
