      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must have documented sources, uncertainty distributions, and sensitivity rankings; Monte Carlo propagation must cover all significant uncertain inputs.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed but only four of nine uncertain hemolysis model parameters were included in the propagation; remaining parameters were fixed at nominal values without sensitivity ranking justification. Achieved level 3 versus required level 5."
